{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Create your own cozy forest!</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Plant Seeds and Watch Them Grow</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/extras/tree_grow_3.gif?t=1737449817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the full lifecycle of trees: seed, sapling, adult tree, dead tree and fallen trunk. Each step creates a different habitat for other plants and animals.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fill Your Forest with Animals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/extras/habitats_2.gif?t=1737449817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each animal has specific habitat needs you have to fullfill before adding them. Squirrels need trees, butterflies need flowers etc.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Click Animals to Make Them Poop and More</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/extras/click_poop_2.gif?t=1737449817\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clicking on animals trigger different behaviors that influence the forest ecosystem: Moose poop, fertilizing the soil. Voles eat tree roots, damaging the tree. Foxes hunt other animals.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737449817","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737449817","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737449817","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968160/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737449817","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Ga